			"description": "<ul><li>A critical feature that makes the monitoring data actionable by alerting users when an issue is detected</li><li>- Users can create and manage notification channels for different services</li><li>- Supports a wide range of notification providers including Email, Slack, Discord, Webhooks, PagerDuty, and Matrix</li><li>- Notifications are triggered based on monitor status changes (e</li><li>g</li><li>, from 'up' to 'down') or when hardware metrics cross pre-defined thresholds</li><li>- Users can test notification configurations to ensure they are working correctly before attaching them to monitors</li></ul>",
