			"description": "<ul><li>Provides efficiency tools for managing a large number of monitors</li><li>- Users can import multiple monitors at once by uploading a CSV file, saving significant time during initial setup</li><li>- A template CSV is provided to guide the user on the required format and available fields</li><li>- All existing monitors can be exported to a CSV file, useful for backups or migrations</li><li>- Superadmins have the ability to delete all monitors for a team in a single action</li></ul>",
